org.kepler.objectmanager.data.db

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.objectmanager.data.DataObjectDescription
      • org.kepler.objectmanager.data.db.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DSTableFieldIFace, DSTableIFace

    public class Entity
extends DataObjectDescription
implements DSTableIFace
    This object represents an TableEntity. A TableEntity stores information about a table of Attributes that is used in a Step in the pipeline.
